搞左成個半月, 大家日日不斷進化, 而家一D舊POST既觀點睇番係會同而家有衝突, 而佢地會好仆街咁定時推呢D POST上黎玩分化, 但其實出POST既當時係真心為大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad62aa58dea64ce6f8dc735d87fe4cfb1d434510","tid":1351512,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:08:23.000Z","msg":"之前AO講果班水軍<br />\n我大概摸到佢地想搞乜了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e81bb8da48f1833b9ab269cf388651c6466aca5","tid":1351512,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:09:17.000Z","msg":"2。x環已經出手，大量水軍打輿論戰，所以各大論壇facebook已經充斥大量打手，今次顧用的是本地打手，人數幾百人。另外，潛伏的「鬼」亦會出動主力抹黑泛民，務求打散整體號召力，以及為建制在即將舉行的區選減壓。"},{"pid":"6fc328f0cc89ee1012f8f382a5e5a7b2d4985c38","tid":1351512,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"041722e553e5722fb20dedc61030a7a2933f1e19","tid":1351512,"uid":270398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:07:06.000Z","msg":"而家再多一樣野, 要學識留意埋推POST果個係邊個, 唔只係睇出POST內容同樓主ID, 特別係D舊POST要特別警覺, 成場抗爭家下搞左成個半月, 大家日日不斷進化, 而家一D舊POST既觀點睇番係會同而家有衝突, 而佢地會好仆街咁定時推呢D POST上黎玩分化, 但其實出POST既當時係真心為大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:10:23.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n佢地會推舊POST"},{"pid":"f7e16f11e1b933777a6c0828f292e65d0dfac0dc","tid":1351512,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:13:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歡迎一毛繼續開/推POST<br />\n我FEEL到係換左批人</span></span>"},{"pid":"fa31a47e89e39d9c528e3b6a01ab498039f738f3","tid":1351512,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:21:35.000Z","msg":"仲有扮假膠post<br />\ne,g, 我係林鄭月娥，你問我答"},{"pid":"54d7a4fd48b5c5761da48293bce0d8dbfe64412e","tid":1351512,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa31a47e89e39d9c528e3b6a01ab498039f738f3","tid":1351512,"uid":179379,"like