,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c80f4128aef602c6b4295e56e95f65e5a2257aa","tid":1351512,"uid":179379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa7a2b60c6423b72cc5d7b8ed7f74d066c0294c9","tid":1351512,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa31a47e89e39d9c528e3b6a01ab498039f738f3","tid":1351512,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:21:35.000Z","msg":"仲有扮假膠post<br />\ne,g, 我係林鄭月娥，你問我答"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:23:27.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n連登不嬲多假膠<br />\n唔代表係一毛<br />\n而家既一毛其實睇落似乎唔了解連登<br />\n又或者高估左連登影響力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:28:33.000Z","msg":"例如呢個 (同一個人嚟)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1282524/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1282524/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348560/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348560/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n假膠唔一定係一毛<br />\n但會有一毛扮假膠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:30:26.000Z","msg":"原來呢條友我一早完全封鎖左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4a3bfe9ae879382f27e3cb5ae82f8faf11ec97","tid":1351512,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bca75271bd046d5c238701d4673b2792f755cc","tid":1351512,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da2ae5fbadd4d131239be8395adcd405cc7946a","tid":1351512,"uid":268692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae0a78e98ec20e227619ad99c037bad96e301d27","tid":1351512,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"好早之前開左係學術台無人睇，咁我索性搬返去時事台<br />\n<br />\n<strong>一毛手法：</strong><br />\n1.一邊做正方，一邊做反方互屌，屌到咁上下就會有傻仔加入<br />\n例如早排既連儂牆同一毛扮熱狗/泛民<br />\n<br />\n2.推舊POST上水，搞到你地失焦<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6uCrrwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6uCrrwW.jpg&h=ea2dad33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.FAKE NEWS 「我個FD話」「聽人講」<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/5VFp1Bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5VFp1Bb.jpg&h=b357f856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拿，而家班一毛就好識拎FACT CHECKED黎做擋箭牌<br />\n唔該用你地個腦諗下邊D野係對我地有利 對我地不利<br />\n邊D係唔需要FACT CHECK都無壞<br />\n唔好一句車埋黎話FACT CHECKED就信到十足十<br />\n網絡世界係好狡滑<br />\n<br />\n4.不停開新聞POST洗底<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/jJFXxWL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJFXxWL.jpg&h=6383711a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.長期覆COMMENT只係打表情，又或者得張圖<br />\n我有幾個長期跟蹤既一毛，高級一毛係甚少開POST防起底<br />\n但係好多時會係你POST出現<br />\n<br />\n6.表面負面撚實際上曲線讚美，唔會見到佢地直接屌中共<br />\n<br />\n7.白痴手法 郁D就話人一毛 賊喊捉賊<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Lohv2F8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLohv2F8.png&h=61979c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留意，話人同俾人話果個都<span style=\"color: red;\">一齊起</span><br />\n連登只能夠起開POST，但係起唔到COMMENT<br />\n呢個時候你就用GOOGLE大法 打佢ID後面加上site:<a href=\"http://lihkg.com\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com</a><br />\n當然呢招對COMMON ID無用 例如我<br />\n不過注意<br />\n起底係俾你知道佢開POST通常係咩取向<br />\n唔係話少開POST＝鬼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>應對方法：</strong><br />\n1.唔好回覆由得個POST沉，一毛不停推POST去到咁上下就會自動收皮<br />\n<br />\n2.唔好睇正負評，連登太多羊仔跟住人行<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">獨立思考，切忌跟風</span></span>。你只要開POST發表意見，變相係助攻帶風向<br />\n<br />\n4.不停推應該推既POST 例如而家就要推上環單野 因為文宣不足 元朗效果已有<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如何對付不斷推POST既一毛撚屌：</strong><br />\n簡單黎講，就係要記低ID<br />\n係同一個POST入面，ID重覆頻率越高代表一毛可能性越大<br />\n至於個POST ID個個唔同咁點呀？<br />\n咁就將焦點擺落樓主度，睇佢D POST/一毛POST再計重覆頻率<br />\n呢招其實好撚豬，因為係變相自爆<br />\n連登有幾個高級一毛我長期跟開<br />\n佢地係唔會經常性係一毛POST出現<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當然，呢D只係佢地招數，唔好諗住捉一毛<br />\n分分鐘捉錯人，只作參考用途</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然，咁唔可能得個守架嘛<br />\n等到你開始分到一毛啦，就可以進行反擊<br />\n以下方法慎用<br />\n<br />\n<strong>反擊操作：</strong><br />\n1.引戰POST，釣魚<br />\n最佳例子：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1330754/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1330754/page/1</a><br />\n入面就有幾隻一毛上水係度互相打飛機<br />\n想學人釣魚之前一定要熟知一毛同埋睇多D呢類POST<br />\n一個唔該就俾一毛騎劫風向<br />\n例如PTT就好撚多釣魚文值得學習<br />\n<br />\n1.1 關於釣魚文：<br />\n樓主通常會開個好撚偏頗既標題同內文<br />\n例如：臨時立法會<br />\nLV1:邊個話搞臨會就係鬼！<br />\nLV2:臨時立法會咪即係變相俾人針<br />\nLV3:臨時立法會乜準備都無想點<br />\nLV4:（對臨會有一定認識同程序 要追哂POST先知）<br />\n然後嘈到一半就會人間蒸發<br />\n留低班人係度互屌<br />\n連登仔對於釣魚文既反應只停留係LV1 <br />\nLV3肯定有一堆正評<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以唔該你地追哂POST先俾正評定負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n2.先發制人<br />\n例如呢篇：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1330511/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1330511/page/1</a><br />\n其實呢條橋前幾日已經有連登仔提過，只不過俾我撈返上水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1317680/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1317680/page/1</a><br />\n風向一旦成功帶走，一毛只可以鳩推POST分散版面焦點<br />\n<br />\n3.假設好不幸咁俾一毛帶風向，咁就要盡快出POST騎劫返轉頭<br />\n騎唔到至少都要55開，有日只係得TVB SOURCE同陳雲就洗到成個版面都係<br />\n呢種情況下標題好重要，點落法自行參透<br />\n<br />\n4.選擇適當戰場，即係話，如果你想屌柒一毛<br />\n就要睇係咩POST入面，如果係垃圾POST膠POST既就唔好同佢嘈即刻BLOCK＋冷處理<br />\n如果係<strong>重要POST</strong>就屌到佢老母都唔認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我試過同一毛嘈到成千個COMMENT<br />\n不過一毛都唔係蠢，佢唔會選擇係重要POST同你嘈<br />\n<br />\n利申：入面既相同LINK唔代表就係一毛，我只係拎黎做例子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:38:28.000Z","msg":"講哂出黎我點搵食呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiGAQ4L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiGAQ4L.jpg&h=f0a80a05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/isx4KpS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fisx4KpS.jpg&h=87aed0c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgsXjYh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgsXjYh.jpg&h=39dcdf13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8RY7HbE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8RY7HbE.jpg&h=9ae1709d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcF6din.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtcF6din.jpg&h=e7688c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Km4F2bK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKm4F2bK.jpg&h=515639af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1VrQHff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1VrQHff.jpg&h=0fd9f27f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">727光復元朗 光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"bb5170aa9a11a06b5ce989f73096a991cc7a76e2","tid":1351512,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed093391d34461012408539cb55415d435329600","tid":1351512,"uid":58841,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"低級釣魚標題例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QPx8u9K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQPx8u9K.jpg&h=b0da12ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:45:25.000Z","msg":"<strong>起底大招：</strong><br />\n如果你平時係連登起底只會睇到開左咩POST<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNB5yH2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNB5yH2.jpg&h=0716d561&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係假如你想起埋佢覆過咩POST<br />\n咁就要用到GOOGLE大法<br />\nID ＋ site:<a href=\"http://lihkg.com\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rk3zr3k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frk3zr3k.jpg&h=a03e5d11&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n如果你望到ID＋時間就係佢既COMMENT<br />\n我CLICK入第三個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wRyPfXo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwRyPfXo.jpg&h=6e2f6c68&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n睇佢既回文就知佢唔係一毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n破解方法：<br />\n我已經知道點拆COMMON ID/改ID既一毛<br />\n所以只能夠唔好開/推POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1643509d4526bc889f8f2d4135856c28baa4735e","tid":1351512,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:09:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57efc61bbff9b485cbe57bf1ff8cfa80e4c26963","tid":1351512,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:12:04.000Z","msg":"我想講你地要平時留意最新回應時間<br />\n我日日都會係呢個時間蒲頭 知道人流係點<br />\n佢呢排特別多一毛出沒<br />\n拉到好下仲係2分鐘前"},{"pid":"07dee2a3e4b05a1d32b2d949b61e93ec5b78265d","tid":1351512,"uid":241869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim